{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You work for an evil mining organisation. With only a shoddy pickaxe to start, you must fulfil your quotas for coal each day, growing and hiring employees to reach your goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361510/extras/SmallMiningOperationGif.gif?t=1737249922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each day is a race to mine as much and as deeply as you can - as on nightfall your quotas must be met and your mine will reset. You will need to efficiently manage your equipment and personnel to meet your ever growing quotas and maximise your profits each day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361510/extras/BombExplodeGif.gif?t=1737249922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your mining operation from the ground up. Hire hundreds of employees. Do whatever it takes to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361510/extras/LargeMiningOperationGif.gif?t=1737249922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deep underground, dungeons and treasure awaits you. Ancient secrets from long-lost civilisations can unlock tools, equipment and even biblical powers to grow your coal mining empire.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737249922","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361510/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737249922","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361510/40dae521892a3fa546fb980543bc0dbb81c8f142/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737249922","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361510/40dae521892a3fa546fb980543bc0dbb81c8f142/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737249